---
title: Paneer and Lentil Coconut Curry with Butter Naan
description: Golden seared paneer is delightful in this lentil dish enriched with coconut milk.  Creamy, filling and comforting, this veggie curry just won't quit! The butter naan provides the perfect vehicle to scoop up every last bite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cari-a-la-noix-de-coco-aux-lentilles-et-au-paneer-c9b963eb.jpg
